room_title: Escape room "A Fisherman's Tale" by Escape Goat in Orlando

room_description: While you were visiting the beaches near Pier 84 you found a message in a bottle that had washed up on the shoreline. It was an SOS leading you to Captain Tracey's Charters that is known to be run by a fisherman who is obsessed with finding lost treasure.
